verbose_text: For example, GrTCP10, GrTCP12, GrTCP14b, GrTCP18b and GrTCP20d were relatively highly expressed in leaf while GrTCP7a, GrTCP7c, GrTCP9b and GrTCP14a were exclusively expressed in shoot at very high level, implying their specific roles in the corresponding tissues (XREF_FIG).
